Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,加油 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,亚丝娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,亚丝娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,站起来 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,我不会输
